1
00:01:31,410 --> 00:01:34,048
=The Glamorous Night=

2
00:01:34,632 --> 00:01:38,935
(Ten years ago)

3
00:02:19,176 --> 00:02:20,217
What are you doing?

4
00:02:21,416 --> 00:02:22,977
Nothing, just taking the bus.

5
00:02:23,296 --> 00:02:24,537
Just taking the bus, right?

6
00:02:24,657 --> 00:02:25,176
Enough.

7
00:02:25,176 --> 00:02:27,736
There's all the space.
Why are you stuck behind her?

8
00:02:27,736 --> 00:02:28,257
Enough.

9
00:02:28,257 --> 00:02:29,176
Stop talking to him.

10
00:02:29,176 --> 00:02:29,977
Stop talking to him.

11
00:02:30,777 --> 00:02:32,057
"Who'd want to rub against you?"

12
00:02:32,057 --> 00:02:33,136
Let's get off the bus.

13
00:02:33,136 --> 00:02:34,217
Make yourself clear.

14
00:02:34,377 --> 00:02:35,337
Tell you what.

15
00:02:35,576 --> 00:02:37,016
If I weren't in a hurry,

16
00:02:37,016 --> 00:02:38,616
I'd curse you out right now.

17
00:02:38,616 --> 00:02:39,136
Enough.

18
00:02:39,136 --> 00:02:40,057
Watch your mouth.

19
00:02:40,057 --> 00:02:41,016
"Lunatic"?

20
00:02:41,016 --> 00:02:42,416
You're calling me a lunatic?

21
00:02:42,736 --> 00:02:44,136
You weren't staring at me?

22
00:02:44,296 --> 00:02:46,136
- Stop staring!
- Don't look at me like that.

23
00:02:46,136 --> 00:02:47,057
I'll call the cops.

24
00:02:47,057 --> 00:02:48,497
I'll have you arrested.

25
00:02:48,497 --> 00:02:49,657
Do you hear me?

26
00:02:49,657 --> 00:02:50,136
Enough.

27
00:02:50,136 --> 00:02:51,016
Still staring at me?

28
00:02:51,016 --> 00:02:51,856
Stop arguing.

29
00:02:52,497 --> 00:02:54,016
It's our first day. We can't be late.

30
00:02:54,257 --> 00:02:55,057
Come on, hurry.

31
00:02:59,208 --> 00:03:04,072
(Be yourself. Awakening. Softhearted.)

32
00:03:06,152 --> 00:03:10,158
=Episode 16=
(Unexpected Interruption)

33
00:03:57,896 --> 00:03:58,977
Up so early today?

34
00:03:59,576 --> 00:04:01,416
The joint internal audit team wants

35
00:04:01,416 --> 00:04:03,296
to talk to everyone
from the sales department.

36
00:04:03,657 --> 00:04:06,296
Someone scheduled me
for 9:30 AM. So lame.

37
00:04:06,616 --> 00:04:07,497
I'm so sleepy.

38
00:04:12,296 --> 00:04:13,176
Where's Weiwei?

39
00:04:13,497 --> 00:04:14,777
Already at school.

40
00:04:14,896 --> 00:04:17,017
She leaves before 7 AM nowadays.

41
00:04:17,496 --> 00:04:18,296
Why?

42
00:04:18,296 --> 00:04:19,577
What do you mean?

43
00:04:19,577 --> 00:04:20,897
She changed schools.

44
00:04:21,337 --> 00:04:24,176
Leaving after 7 AM means heavy traffic,
and she'd be late.

45
00:04:25,416 --> 00:04:26,736
What kind of mom doesn't know

46
00:04:27,296 --> 00:04:29,017
her daughter has changed schools?

47
00:04:31,616 --> 00:04:32,736
There's much I don't know.

48
00:04:33,097 --> 00:04:34,056
That's it. I'm off.

49
00:04:36,017 --> 00:04:36,416
What...

50
00:04:40,816 --> 00:04:42,056
She's so busy nowadays?

51
00:04:42,457 --> 00:04:43,777
Can't even have breakfast?

52
00:04:44,232 --> 00:04:47,208
(Yuehai, Teemall)

53
00:05:30,337 --> 00:05:31,176
Mrs. Jin, please.

54
00:05:32,616 --> 00:05:33,337
Mrs. Jin.

55
00:05:33,337 --> 00:05:34,416
Come on in, please.

56
00:05:34,616 --> 00:05:35,777
Nice office you have here.

57
00:05:41,296 --> 00:05:43,296
I've seen enough homewreckers like you.

58
00:05:43,977 --> 00:05:45,537
I'm hanging a peach wood sword here

59
00:05:45,856 --> 00:05:47,496
to ward off hussies like you.

60
00:05:58,537 --> 00:05:59,217
Jiawei.

61
00:05:59,457 --> 00:06:00,337
You look good.

62
00:06:02,097 --> 00:06:02,936
I'm Yang Huiling.

63
00:06:03,977 --> 00:06:06,056
The internal audit team
has such a pretty girl?

64
00:06:07,416 --> 00:06:09,337
You handle the ladies.

65
00:06:10,657 --> 00:06:11,496
Just a second.

66
00:06:12,097 --> 00:06:17,697
Quick question. Do you interrogate
every salesperson like this?

67
00:06:17,856 --> 00:06:19,017
Or is it just me?

68
00:06:19,416 --> 00:06:20,537
I don't get it.

69
00:06:20,537 --> 00:06:24,176
I've already submitted
all the data, spreadsheets,

70
00:06:24,176 --> 00:06:25,657
and self-assessment declarations

71
00:06:26,017 --> 00:06:27,616
you asked for earlier.

72
00:06:28,097 --> 00:06:29,097
Is there a problem?

73
00:06:29,616 --> 00:06:30,897
Let's cut to the chase.

74
00:06:31,457 --> 00:06:34,936
What is your relationship with Shen Mo
from Lingyang Industrial?

75
00:06:36,936 --> 00:06:38,176
Why are you asking that?

76
00:06:38,337 --> 00:06:40,137
Shen Mo is a tier-one distributor.

77
00:06:40,457 --> 00:06:43,296
We need to know his relationship
with our sales personnel.

78
00:06:43,856 --> 00:06:45,897
He's just a distributor I work with.

79
00:06:45,977 --> 00:06:48,897
But someone reported
that you're dating him.

80
00:06:49,736 --> 00:06:50,697
We mean no harm.

81
00:06:51,217 --> 00:06:53,416
But if this is true,

82
00:06:53,457 --> 00:06:56,296
it creates a conflict of interest.

83
00:06:56,296 --> 00:06:57,496
Nonsense.

84
00:06:58,097 --> 00:06:59,657
We're just business partners.

85
00:07:00,777 --> 00:07:02,296
Did someone gossip to you?

86
00:07:02,537 --> 00:07:03,528
That's not your concern.

87
00:07:03,777 --> 00:07:05,657
We have ways to gather information.

88
00:07:06,496 --> 00:07:11,936
Please fill out the form
about your interactions with Mr. Shen.

89
00:07:27,097 --> 00:07:28,416
It doesn't make sense, does it?

90
00:07:29,856 --> 00:07:30,897
One more form for her.

91
00:07:32,457 --> 00:07:34,577
What? That was about me?

92
00:07:34,777 --> 00:07:35,457
What did I do?

93
00:07:35,537 --> 00:07:38,017
We'll need you
to fill out another form to explain

94
00:07:38,416 --> 00:07:42,056
your relationship with Jin Linsheng
from Minghui Construction.

95
00:07:42,457 --> 00:07:43,337
Jin?

96
00:07:49,577 --> 00:07:50,376
Danning.

97
00:07:50,616 --> 00:07:52,017
But before that, please...

98
00:07:52,017 --> 00:07:56,337
Ms. Qi, did someone
say something about me?

99
00:07:56,977 --> 00:07:57,736
No.

100
00:07:57,736 --> 00:07:59,296
Yes, I did.

101
00:07:59,777 --> 00:08:01,217
I'm filing a complaint against you.

102
00:08:01,217 --> 00:08:02,097
Against me?

103
00:08:02,897 --> 00:08:03,856
About what?

104
00:08:03,856 --> 00:08:04,736
Trying to slander me?

105
00:08:05,337 --> 00:08:06,856
Did you bring your peach wood sword

106
00:08:07,176 --> 00:08:08,256
and that dog of yours?

107
00:08:08,416 --> 00:08:10,537
I'm reporting you
for accepting gifts from clients.

108
00:08:10,537 --> 00:08:11,337
What?

109
00:08:11,337 --> 00:08:12,017
What?

110
00:08:12,017 --> 00:08:12,856
Playing dumb?

111
00:08:12,856 --> 00:08:14,856
That was a very expensive handbag.

112
00:08:14,856 --> 00:08:17,416
How could a lowly salesperson
just accept it?

113
00:08:17,416 --> 00:08:20,296
Aren't you afraid
of karma for such greed?

114
00:08:20,296 --> 00:08:22,176
Let's talk in the office, okay?

115
00:08:22,176 --> 00:08:22,736
Come on.

116
00:08:22,736 --> 00:08:23,897
I don't know what you mean.

117
00:08:23,897 --> 00:08:26,457
First, I've never
accepted any improper gifts.

118
00:08:26,457 --> 00:08:30,856
Second, I was actually
mistreated by a client for no reason.

119
00:08:31,217 --> 00:08:34,297
Ms. Qi, since you're here,
I'm filing a complaint.

120
00:08:34,297 --> 00:08:34,856
What?

121
00:08:35,177 --> 00:08:36,337
About what?

122
00:08:36,417 --> 00:08:37,337
Last month,

123
00:08:37,776 --> 00:08:40,577
when I delivered goods to her house,
she set her dog on me.

124
00:08:41,937 --> 00:08:42,457
Look.

125
00:08:44,217 --> 00:08:45,417
Everyone, look.

126
00:08:47,856 --> 00:08:49,217
This is the bite mark I got

127
00:08:49,656 --> 00:08:51,457
when she set her dog on me at her house

128
00:08:51,457 --> 00:08:52,337
last month.

129
00:08:53,217 --> 00:08:54,776
After stitches, it looks like this.

130
00:08:56,217 --> 00:08:57,217
Over a dozen stitches.

131
00:08:57,337 --> 00:08:58,457
And I got rabies shots.

132
00:08:58,616 --> 00:09:00,776
The worst part is the scar.

133
00:09:00,776 --> 00:09:02,217
No more short sleeves in summer.

134
00:09:02,217 --> 00:09:02,817
What do I do?

135
00:09:03,016 --> 00:09:04,297
Is she telling the truth?

136
00:09:05,097 --> 00:09:06,217
So what if it is true?

137
00:09:06,457 --> 00:09:08,457
A homewrecker like her deserves this.

138
00:09:09,616 --> 00:09:11,457
Fine, say it again.

139
00:09:12,217 --> 00:09:13,457
I'll record it

140
00:09:13,457 --> 00:09:14,656
and call the police, okay?

141
00:09:14,817 --> 00:09:15,856
Say it if you dare.

142
00:09:15,856 --> 00:09:16,736
Why should I

143
00:09:16,736 --> 00:09:17,776
listen to you?

144
00:09:19,217 --> 00:09:19,977
Scared now?

145
00:09:20,776 --> 00:09:22,256
Because if I call the police,

146
00:09:22,616 --> 00:09:23,896
they will prove

147
00:09:23,896 --> 00:09:26,337
that there is nothing
between your husband and me.

148
00:09:26,337 --> 00:09:29,217
I didn't even step inside your house,
but you set your dog on me.

149
00:09:29,217 --> 00:09:30,776
And now you're publicly slandering me.

150
00:09:30,776 --> 00:09:31,736
How did I slander you?

151
00:09:32,217 --> 00:09:32,896
That's too much.

152
00:09:32,896 --> 00:09:34,736
Ms. Qi, do you see?

153
00:09:35,417 --> 00:09:37,896
I wanted to let it go to keep the peace.

154
00:09:37,896 --> 00:09:39,656
I thought, well, she's a client.

155
00:09:39,656 --> 00:09:41,016
But now she's making a scene.

156
00:09:41,016 --> 00:09:42,616
I can't take it anymore, Ms. Qi.

157
00:09:42,616 --> 00:09:44,656
Will the company stand up for me?

158
00:09:45,097 --> 00:09:45,616
Of course.

159
00:09:46,016 --> 00:09:46,776
Mrs. Jin.

160
00:09:47,457 --> 00:09:48,856
This is our office building.

161
00:09:49,016 --> 00:09:50,656
You can't treat my employee like this.

162
00:09:51,217 --> 00:09:52,977
You may be an important client,

163
00:09:52,977 --> 00:09:54,776
but if what she said is true,

164
00:09:54,776 --> 00:09:55,297
I reserve

165
00:09:55,297 --> 00:09:56,376
the right to sue you.

166
00:10:05,217 --> 00:10:06,856
She hit me with her handbag.

167
00:10:07,937 --> 00:10:08,736
That's enough.

168
00:10:08,736 --> 00:10:09,496
Guys, look.

169
00:10:09,856 --> 00:10:10,457
Enough.

170
00:10:12,097 --> 00:10:14,656
The company will protect you, okay?

171
00:10:15,057 --> 00:10:16,376
Everyone, back to work.

172
00:10:16,736 --> 00:10:17,736
It's over.

173
00:10:18,977 --> 00:10:20,016
Can I buy you a coffee?

174
00:10:20,177 --> 00:10:21,057
Let's talk privately.

175
00:10:23,736 --> 00:10:26,297
Is there anything going on
between you and Jin Linsheng?

176
00:10:28,256 --> 00:10:30,577
Didn't I just make it clear?

177
00:10:30,937 --> 00:10:33,856
Jin Linsheng and I
are completely innocent.

178
00:10:33,856 --> 00:10:35,776
His wife is the one causing trouble.

179
00:10:37,736 --> 00:10:38,536
Liang Danning.

180
00:10:39,736 --> 00:10:40,856
We're alone here.

181
00:10:41,577 --> 00:10:42,817
You can tell the truth.

182
00:10:43,616 --> 00:10:46,856
I knew that she set her dog on you
the very next day.

183
00:10:46,856 --> 00:10:49,736
I also know that Jin Linsheng
bought you a Hermes Birkin

184
00:10:49,736 --> 00:10:51,136
and ordered a lot of wine.

185
00:10:51,136 --> 00:10:53,097
At the Nansha Garden VIP dinner,

186
00:10:53,097 --> 00:10:54,656
he only went to support you.

187
00:10:54,856 --> 00:10:56,457
I don't care about any of those.

188
00:10:56,457 --> 00:10:57,776
I don't even want to know.

189
00:10:58,457 --> 00:11:02,136
But now, his wife has come storming in.

190
00:11:02,457 --> 00:11:04,016
It may damage our reputation.

191
00:11:04,217 --> 00:11:06,097
So I have to ask you.

192
00:11:06,697 --> 00:11:08,817
Are you two in a romantic relationship?

193
00:11:08,817 --> 00:11:09,376
No.

194
00:11:09,977 --> 00:11:13,016
There is nothing
between Jin Linsheng and me.

195
00:11:16,697 --> 00:11:18,256
Then how do you explain that bag?

196
00:11:18,736 --> 00:11:20,097
That's simple.

197
00:11:20,616 --> 00:11:22,496
Jin Linsheng gave me that to apologize.

198
00:11:22,616 --> 00:11:25,097
It covers the medical bills
and compensation.

199
00:11:25,217 --> 00:11:26,536
If you don't believe me,

200
00:11:27,097 --> 00:11:28,097
I can arrange a meeting

201
00:11:28,097 --> 00:11:29,417
with him, okay?

202
00:11:30,256 --> 00:11:31,097
What about Shen Mo?

203
00:11:31,856 --> 00:11:33,057
Are you two dating?

204
00:11:35,977 --> 00:11:36,577
No.

205
00:11:37,736 --> 00:11:39,136
If you don't believe me, I...

206
00:11:39,720 --> 00:11:41,528
(Shen Mo)

207
00:11:44,376 --> 00:11:45,057
Want to talk?

208
00:11:48,256 --> 00:11:49,057
I'll head off now.

209
00:11:51,856 --> 00:11:52,417
Mr. Shen.

210
00:11:53,736 --> 00:11:54,856
I'm not at the company.

211
00:11:55,177 --> 00:11:58,057
I'm at the coffee shop downstairs.
Yeah, I'm listening.

212
00:11:58,577 --> 00:11:59,097
What?

213
00:11:59,937 --> 00:12:02,776
Liang Danning fought with a client
on the 24th floor?

214
00:12:04,097 --> 00:12:04,896
Which client?

215
00:12:05,097 --> 00:12:05,937
I'm not sure.

216
00:12:06,097 --> 00:12:07,256
I heard it's a female client.

217
00:12:10,217 --> 00:12:11,376
Okay, get back to work.

218
00:12:19,337 --> 00:12:20,337
Where are you?

219
00:12:20,616 --> 00:12:21,616
I've already left.

220
00:12:21,616 --> 00:12:25,256
I just made a scene in front of
all the big shots on the 24th floor.

221
00:12:25,256 --> 00:12:26,417
The higher-ups...

222
00:12:26,977 --> 00:12:28,496
Such a pity you missed it.

223
00:12:28,616 --> 00:12:30,297
It was awesome.

224
00:12:31,736 --> 00:12:33,057
Not a female client.

225
00:12:33,057 --> 00:12:34,217
It was Jin Linsheng's wife.

226
00:12:34,337 --> 00:12:35,577
The one who set her dog on me.

227
00:12:35,977 --> 00:12:38,457
Why did she suddenly come
to look for trouble?

228
00:12:38,457 --> 00:12:40,097
You're not seeing Jin Linsheng.

229
00:12:41,856 --> 00:12:42,937
Someone's playing tricks?

230
00:12:43,217 --> 00:12:44,656
Right on.

231
00:12:44,656 --> 00:12:45,856
It's Yao Xiaohui.

232
00:12:46,496 --> 00:12:48,016
After the divorce,

233
00:12:48,496 --> 00:12:49,977
he couldn't swallow his pride

234
00:12:49,977 --> 00:12:51,457
and told everyone I was cheating.

235
00:12:51,457 --> 00:12:52,577
He even used that handbag

236
00:12:52,577 --> 00:12:53,776
as proof of my being kept.

237
00:12:54,616 --> 00:12:55,337
It just happened

238
00:12:56,016 --> 00:13:00,417
that one of his gambling buddies
worked as a salesman for that brand.

239
00:13:00,776 --> 00:13:03,217
And Mrs. Jin happened
to be his VIP client.

240
00:13:03,616 --> 00:13:06,577
Eventually, the rumors twisted
into me being kept by Jin Linsheng.

241
00:13:06,977 --> 00:13:09,577
So that crazy woman came over here
like a mad bull.

242
00:13:10,217 --> 00:13:11,856
But do you know what's the worst?

243
00:13:12,457 --> 00:13:15,616
She didn't complain
about my relationship with her husband.

244
00:13:15,616 --> 00:13:18,656
She reported me for accepting
improper gifts from clients.

245
00:13:18,977 --> 00:13:21,097
While love affairs are taboo,

246
00:13:21,097 --> 00:13:22,297
they are just taboo.

247
00:13:22,616 --> 00:13:25,577
But accepting improper gifts
is a fireable offense.

248
00:13:25,656 --> 00:13:27,577
Cross the line
and your career's finished.

249
00:13:30,736 --> 00:13:33,097
How did you figure this out so fast?

250
00:13:34,977 --> 00:13:36,536
Shen Mo told me.

251
00:13:37,136 --> 00:13:39,337
The moment that crazy woman came,

252
00:13:39,337 --> 00:13:40,457
he heard about it.

253
00:13:41,057 --> 00:13:42,217
Not sure who informed him.

254
00:13:42,817 --> 00:13:45,297
I was thinking
whether to call and complain.

255
00:13:45,457 --> 00:13:47,136
Then he called me first.

256
00:13:47,457 --> 00:13:48,097
Okay.

257
00:13:48,736 --> 00:13:49,616
I bet

258
00:13:49,616 --> 00:13:51,856
Shen Mo will get the problem solved
right away.

259
00:13:52,736 --> 00:13:53,856
I'll head to a meeting.

260
00:13:53,856 --> 00:13:54,656
Call you later.

261
00:13:54,817 --> 00:13:55,457
Bye.

262
00:14:02,217 --> 00:14:03,977
You were pretty cocky earlier.

263
00:14:10,977 --> 00:14:12,057
I'm talking about you.

264
00:14:12,057 --> 00:14:13,097
Are you insane?

265
00:14:20,337 --> 00:14:21,856
Mrs. Jin.

266
00:14:22,136 --> 00:14:24,577
There's nothing between Mr. Jin and me.

267
00:14:24,736 --> 00:14:25,697
You saw what happened.

268
00:14:25,697 --> 00:14:27,097
I left the wine at your doorstep

269
00:14:27,097 --> 00:14:28,217
and didn't even enter...

270
00:14:36,896 --> 00:14:37,417
What...

271
00:14:39,177 --> 00:14:40,496
How dare you slap me?

272
00:14:40,817 --> 00:14:41,736
Let go! I'll kill you!

273
00:14:41,736 --> 00:14:42,697
You homewrecker!

274
00:14:42,697 --> 00:14:43,337
Take that!

275
00:14:43,337 --> 00:14:44,736
Why are you doing this to her?

276
00:14:44,736 --> 00:14:46,256
This woman seduced my husband!

277
00:14:46,256 --> 00:14:46,977
No.

278
00:14:46,977 --> 00:14:48,856
She's seducing my dad
to become my stepmother.

279
00:14:48,856 --> 00:14:49,616
What nonsense!

280
00:14:49,616 --> 00:14:51,177
Shut up!

281
00:14:51,457 --> 00:14:52,457
Check out the group chat.

282
00:14:52,457 --> 00:14:53,297
I rushed here.

283
00:14:59,097 --> 00:15:00,097
Why did you come?

284
00:15:00,097 --> 00:15:01,177
Go find her.

285
00:15:06,616 --> 00:15:08,097
It happened right here.

286
00:15:09,337 --> 00:15:10,736
Should we call the police?

287
00:15:12,496 --> 00:15:13,376
Keep searching.

288
00:15:13,697 --> 00:15:14,616
Check up ahead.

289
00:15:14,616 --> 00:15:14,896
Okay.

290
00:15:20,376 --> 00:15:21,376
No, this is too slow.

291
00:15:21,616 --> 00:15:23,337
Yu Wei'e, go there. Tommy, go there.

292
00:15:25,977 --> 00:15:27,097
I can't reach Liang Danning.

293
00:15:27,256 --> 00:15:27,977
Me neither.

294
00:15:29,337 --> 00:15:30,937
- I'll call Shen Mo.
- Don't.

295
00:15:31,217 --> 00:15:32,656
Liang Danning might not want you to.

296
00:15:32,856 --> 00:15:33,496
Why not?

297
00:15:33,817 --> 00:15:34,577
He's Shen Mo.

298
00:15:34,577 --> 00:15:35,736
Not just any guy.

299
00:15:35,856 --> 00:15:38,577
Jin Linsheng is his friend
and business partner.

300
00:15:39,256 --> 00:15:41,977
You don't think Shen Mo
will help Liang Danning?

301
00:15:41,977 --> 00:15:43,496
I think Shen Mo dislikes you.

302
00:15:43,496 --> 00:15:44,977
You calling would only backfire.

303
00:15:49,337 --> 00:15:49,896
It's her.

304
00:15:52,856 --> 00:15:53,577
Where are you?

305
00:15:53,736 --> 00:15:55,457
I'm nearby.

306
00:15:56,937 --> 00:15:58,297
It was a mess. I didn't hear.

307
00:15:58,977 --> 00:16:00,337
Are you okay?

308
00:16:00,616 --> 00:16:03,057
I'm fine. It was just a slap.
How bad could it be?

309
00:16:03,817 --> 00:16:04,977
Guess who saved me.

310
00:16:04,977 --> 00:16:06,097
You won't believe it.

311
00:16:06,097 --> 00:16:06,896
Who?

312
00:16:07,097 --> 00:16:08,217
Qi Youlan.

313
00:16:08,256 --> 00:16:09,376
Let go.

314
00:16:09,376 --> 00:16:11,697
- The police are here.
- Shut up.

315
00:16:12,097 --> 00:16:14,016
Let her go.

316
00:16:14,217 --> 00:16:14,856
Get off her!

317
00:16:14,856 --> 00:16:15,616
Who is it?

318
00:16:15,697 --> 00:16:16,457
Let her go.

319
00:16:17,457 --> 00:16:18,297
I'll call the police.

320
00:16:18,496 --> 00:16:19,736
We're all people of standing.

321
00:16:19,736 --> 00:16:21,577
Is it you or your husband
who has no shame?

322
00:16:27,097 --> 00:16:28,337
Go away. Stop filming.

323
00:16:29,577 --> 00:16:30,457
She just left?

324
00:17:02,817 --> 00:17:03,337
Yeah.

325
00:17:04,137 --> 00:17:05,736
We were having coffee together.

326
00:17:06,256 --> 00:17:08,096
But she came out a bit later than me.

327
00:17:08,096 --> 00:17:09,177
Somehow she saw us.

328
00:17:09,496 --> 00:17:10,296
She stood by me.

329
00:17:10,937 --> 00:17:12,576
Well, that's a relief.

330
00:17:14,977 --> 00:17:15,736
It's okay now.

331
00:17:17,417 --> 00:17:19,377
She said Qi Youlan saved her.

332
00:17:19,457 --> 00:17:20,457
How strange.

333
00:17:23,576 --> 00:17:24,617
I don't want to go back.

334
00:17:24,857 --> 00:17:26,256
Tell Peter that I have

335
00:17:26,256 --> 00:17:26,977
a headache.

336
00:17:28,857 --> 00:17:32,377
Zhao Mei.
I don't want to go back, either.

337
00:17:42,857 --> 00:17:44,536
Danning, what treatment
are we doing today?

338
00:17:45,336 --> 00:17:47,617
I'd like a facial soothing treatment.

339
00:17:47,617 --> 00:17:49,256
And a meridian scraping for my body.

340
00:17:49,736 --> 00:17:50,897
I'll get things ready.

341
00:17:59,528 --> 00:18:02,779
(Shen Mo)

342
00:18:15,857 --> 00:18:16,617
This is for you.

343
00:18:18,336 --> 00:18:19,176
I didn't order this.

344
00:18:20,336 --> 00:18:22,457
To commemorate
your hundredth visit here.

345
00:18:24,336 --> 00:18:25,177
How do you remember?

346
00:18:26,336 --> 00:18:27,096
Of course I do.

347
00:18:27,457 --> 00:18:28,576
Because I'm teasing you.

348
00:18:29,457 --> 00:18:30,217
I'm sorry.

349
00:18:30,457 --> 00:18:31,617
Enjoy yourselves.

350
00:18:31,617 --> 00:18:33,776
Tell me if you need anything.

351
00:18:33,937 --> 00:18:34,816
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

352
00:18:43,857 --> 00:18:45,137
She's into you.

353
00:18:48,096 --> 00:18:49,296
You're in the mood for that?

354
00:18:54,816 --> 00:18:56,177
Do you know Jin Linsheng?

355
00:18:58,496 --> 00:18:59,296
Kind of.

356
00:19:01,697 --> 00:19:02,857
Jin Linsheng

357
00:19:03,937 --> 00:19:05,096
came from a poor background.

358
00:19:06,417 --> 00:19:08,496
He was so poor
that he had to beg for money.

359
00:19:09,736 --> 00:19:11,576
His wife ran a restaurant back then.

360
00:19:12,296 --> 00:19:14,977
They met when he worked
at her restaurant.

361
00:19:16,256 --> 00:19:19,496
She provided the first investment
for his business.

362
00:19:21,177 --> 00:19:22,617
No wonder he sticks by her side

363
00:19:22,617 --> 00:19:23,857
even though her wife is crazy.

364
00:19:26,016 --> 00:19:26,977
He has no choice.

365
00:19:29,496 --> 00:19:30,857
What do you mean?

366
00:19:31,617 --> 00:19:34,177
He has benefited.
It's only fair he takes responsibility.

367
00:19:35,336 --> 00:19:37,937
Since he knows his wife is paranoid,

368
00:19:37,937 --> 00:19:39,296
he should keep her in line

369
00:19:39,296 --> 00:19:40,377
to not cause trouble.

370
00:19:41,576 --> 00:19:42,377
I'm telling you.

371
00:19:42,576 --> 00:19:45,056
That's why couples
should be well-matched.

372
00:19:45,056 --> 00:19:46,177
Charity cases don't work.

373
00:19:58,977 --> 00:19:59,496
(Oh no.)

374
00:20:00,137 --> 00:20:03,536
(Dong Yue definitely doesn't want to
hear the phrase "well-matched".)

375
00:20:05,816 --> 00:20:08,576
What did Liang Danning do wrong?

376
00:20:09,377 --> 00:20:10,496
She was just working.

377
00:20:10,496 --> 00:20:11,697
And she got slapped.

378
00:20:12,096 --> 00:20:13,256
I feel so bad for her.

379
00:20:25,897 --> 00:20:29,417
You emailed Peter
to have Jin Linsheng blacklisted?

380
00:20:29,816 --> 00:20:31,776
I've kicked him out
of the client group chat.

381
00:20:32,096 --> 00:20:34,184
If his wife were in it,
I'd have kicked her out too.

382
00:20:36,056 --> 00:20:36,857
Really?

383
00:20:41,617 --> 00:20:43,576
Here, a toast to you.

384
00:20:44,336 --> 00:20:44,977
Well done.

385
00:20:47,336 --> 00:20:49,177
No need. Liang Danning works under me.

386
00:20:49,776 --> 00:20:51,816
Her being bullied
is the same as me being bullied.

387
00:20:52,937 --> 00:20:53,816
It's not the same.

388
00:20:55,137 --> 00:20:56,496
I remember that a few years ago,

389
00:20:56,776 --> 00:21:00,336
a salesperson under Tang Lide
got into a fight

390
00:21:00,657 --> 00:21:02,697
with a client at the dinner table.

391
00:21:03,096 --> 00:21:05,137
That client called his driver over

392
00:21:05,377 --> 00:21:06,776
and beat up that salesperson.

393
00:21:07,496 --> 00:21:08,977
You weren't with us back then.

394
00:21:09,697 --> 00:21:11,137
He was beaten terribly.

395
00:21:11,137 --> 00:21:12,617
Blood gushed from his nostrils.

396
00:21:14,336 --> 00:21:17,417
Then Xu negotiated the compensation.

397
00:21:17,417 --> 00:21:19,400
50,000 from the company.
50,000 from the client.

398
00:21:19,617 --> 00:21:21,857
But that salesperson resigned
within two months.

399
00:21:22,816 --> 00:21:24,576
And the client remained.

400
00:21:25,496 --> 00:21:26,377
I'm not Tang Lide.

401
00:21:29,296 --> 00:21:30,137
I'm not Xu either.

402
00:21:34,617 --> 00:21:36,937
But Jin Linsheng is Shen Mo's friend.

403
00:21:38,016 --> 00:21:39,457
What if you offend Shen Mo?

404
00:21:41,496 --> 00:21:43,177
This isn't the first time, anyway.

405
00:21:48,056 --> 00:21:49,096
Be more specific.

406
00:21:54,016 --> 00:21:54,937
I'm not telling you.

407
00:22:01,096 --> 00:22:02,256
Mom, you're back.

408
00:22:02,697 --> 00:22:03,697
Yeah, I'm back.

409
00:22:07,576 --> 00:22:08,496
You're doing homework?

410
00:22:10,617 --> 00:22:12,217
Lift your head a bit, sweetie.

411
00:22:12,857 --> 00:22:14,096
You're back so early today.

412
00:22:14,776 --> 00:22:15,536
See?

413
00:22:15,617 --> 00:22:18,217
Those are gifts from Mr. Shen.

414
00:22:19,816 --> 00:22:21,016
When were they delivered?

415
00:22:21,736 --> 00:22:23,536
A driver came at 6 PM,

416
00:22:23,697 --> 00:22:24,576
carrying all those.

417
00:22:24,897 --> 00:22:26,736
I thought to myself, "So many things!"

418
00:22:27,217 --> 00:22:28,016
Then I looked again.

419
00:22:28,377 --> 00:22:29,177
Dried abalone.

420
00:22:29,177 --> 00:22:30,217
Premium quality.

421
00:22:31,177 --> 00:22:33,096
I meant to call you about it.

422
00:22:33,377 --> 00:22:34,977
But we got some customers.

423
00:22:35,296 --> 00:22:36,736
I got busy and forgot.

424
00:22:37,296 --> 00:22:38,857
So who is Mr. Shen?

425
00:22:40,857 --> 00:22:41,977
Is he your boyfriend?

426
00:22:42,496 --> 00:22:44,457
No, he's just a client.

427
00:22:44,736 --> 00:22:45,657
You think I'm silly?

428
00:22:46,137 --> 00:22:47,977
What client would be that generous?

429
00:23:00,417 --> 00:23:02,137
I came home and found many dried goods.

430
00:23:02,137 --> 00:23:02,937
Are they from you?

431
00:23:03,897 --> 00:23:04,897
For consolation?

432
00:23:05,177 --> 00:23:05,617
Yeah.

433
00:23:06,336 --> 00:23:07,417
I was about to call you.

434
00:23:09,137 --> 00:23:11,296
I heard what Jin's wife did.

435
00:23:12,056 --> 00:23:12,977
You've been wronged.

436
00:23:13,617 --> 00:23:14,736
I'll handle this.

437
00:23:15,137 --> 00:23:17,897
I'll ask Jin to make it up to you.

438
00:23:24,336 --> 00:23:25,056
Where are you?

439
00:23:25,217 --> 00:23:25,977
I want to see you.

440
00:23:32,256 --> 00:23:32,857
Which way?

441
00:23:34,336 --> 00:23:34,897
Where are we

442
00:23:35,096 --> 00:23:35,776
going to walk?

443
00:23:36,776 --> 00:23:37,857
When did you find out?

444
00:23:38,857 --> 00:23:40,857
I was slapped around 2 PM.

445
00:23:41,336 --> 00:23:43,177
We had just hung up before that.

446
00:23:43,177 --> 00:23:45,576
You knew Jin Linsheng's wife
came after me.

447
00:23:45,576 --> 00:23:46,937
You said you'd talk to him.

448
00:23:47,096 --> 00:23:49,697
It's already 9:55 PM.

449
00:23:49,897 --> 00:23:51,296
When did you learn I was slapped?

450
00:23:52,776 --> 00:23:54,344
About half an hour after it happened.

451
00:23:55,377 --> 00:23:57,336
Why didn't you call me then?

452
00:23:57,336 --> 00:23:58,576
Why didn't you come to me?

453
00:23:58,697 --> 00:24:00,617
You sent the driver to deliver things.

454
00:24:00,937 --> 00:24:01,776
Were you waiting

455
00:24:03,096 --> 00:24:04,296
for me to beg for help?

456
00:24:04,296 --> 00:24:05,137
Yeah.

457
00:24:05,857 --> 00:24:07,177
Why didn't you ask me for help?

458
00:24:07,617 --> 00:24:09,776
You should've called me on the spot.

459
00:24:09,776 --> 00:24:11,697
Because I don't trust you.

460
00:24:12,137 --> 00:24:13,977
I don't believe you can do me justice.

461
00:24:15,377 --> 00:24:15,977
This afternoon,

462
00:24:18,217 --> 00:24:20,457
when Jin came to apologize,

463
00:24:20,617 --> 00:24:23,177
I told him to skip the excuses

464
00:24:23,617 --> 00:24:26,296
and get his mentally ill wife
for treatment

465
00:24:26,536 --> 00:24:27,417
lest she harm others.

466
00:24:28,776 --> 00:24:30,377
He already agreed to place

467
00:24:30,977 --> 00:24:33,056
a five-million-yuan order next week.

468
00:24:33,816 --> 00:24:34,776
Are you okay with that?

469
00:24:37,377 --> 00:24:38,177
Sounds okay.

470
00:24:38,857 --> 00:24:40,096
Why would I have a problem?

471
00:24:40,576 --> 00:24:41,377
I'll take the order.

472
00:24:41,617 --> 00:24:42,336
Let's break up.

473
00:24:43,457 --> 00:24:44,576
Stop this.

474
00:24:45,096 --> 00:24:46,617
Stop beating around the bush.

475
00:24:46,617 --> 00:24:47,496
Just speak your mind.

476
00:24:47,776 --> 00:24:48,576
Seriously?

477
00:24:48,576 --> 00:24:49,977
You're the one avoiding the issue!

478
00:24:50,617 --> 00:24:52,016
I was the one slapped in public.

479
00:24:52,417 --> 00:24:54,776
I was publicly humiliated.

480
00:24:55,096 --> 00:24:57,496
But Jin apologized to you.

481
00:24:57,496 --> 00:24:58,736
He groveled to you.

482
00:24:58,937 --> 00:25:00,617
I was the victim.

483
00:25:01,056 --> 00:25:03,016
Are you all insane?

484
00:25:03,016 --> 00:25:04,016
What do you want then?

485
00:25:04,296 --> 00:25:06,177
I can make them apologize to you.

486
00:25:06,177 --> 00:25:06,897
What do I want?

487
00:25:06,897 --> 00:25:08,457
I want you to beat Jin Linsheng.

488
00:25:08,776 --> 00:25:09,657
His wife hit me.

489
00:25:09,657 --> 00:25:10,576
So you hit him.

490
00:25:10,776 --> 00:25:12,576
And I want you
to cut ties with him. Will you?

491
00:25:12,977 --> 00:25:14,776
You're not thinking clearly right now.

492
00:25:14,776 --> 00:25:16,096
(At this moment, I realized)

493
00:25:16,096 --> 00:25:18,776
(that Shen Mo had no idea
why I was so angry.)

494
00:25:19,776 --> 00:25:20,536
(To him,)

495
00:25:21,137 --> 00:25:22,496
(it was only natural)

496
00:25:22,776 --> 00:25:25,857
(that Jin Linsheng apologized to him
for what had happened to me.)

497
00:25:26,576 --> 00:25:27,617
(But I knew)

498
00:25:28,256 --> 00:25:30,657
(that if I weren't
Shen Mo's girlfriend,)

499
00:25:30,857 --> 00:25:32,857
(but a random salesperson at GST,)

500
00:25:33,377 --> 00:25:35,857
(then Jin Linsheng
must apologize to me in person)

501
00:25:35,857 --> 00:25:37,217
(and negotiate with me.)

502
00:25:37,776 --> 00:25:40,417
(I wouldn't be waiting
for others to tell me)

503
00:25:40,937 --> 00:25:43,296
(how much compensation I'd get)

504
00:25:43,296 --> 00:25:44,576
(or what the outcome would be.)

505
00:25:45,457 --> 00:25:47,377
(I found a boyfriend like Shen Mo,)

506
00:25:47,776 --> 00:25:49,217
(but lost my own identity)

507
00:25:49,576 --> 00:25:51,016
(as Liang Danning.)

508
00:25:51,937 --> 00:25:53,377
(The world is indeed fair.)

509
00:25:53,937 --> 00:25:55,528
(I've never been that clear-headed.)

510
00:25:55,897 --> 00:25:56,816
(I need to break up.)

511
00:26:08,177 --> 00:26:10,776
I think he mentioned
this company when we first got married.

512
00:26:11,536 --> 00:26:13,296
But I didn't know he had shares.

513
00:26:14,137 --> 00:26:16,857
It was just founded when you married.

514
00:26:17,697 --> 00:26:19,617
Perhaps he didn't take it seriously.

515
00:26:20,857 --> 00:26:22,096
But now it's different.

516
00:26:22,697 --> 00:26:24,816
A listed company wants to acquire them

517
00:26:25,417 --> 00:26:27,056
with a valuation of 500 million.

518
00:26:27,897 --> 00:26:29,296
So that 3 percent means 15 million.

519
00:26:29,536 --> 00:26:29,977
Yes.

520
00:26:31,256 --> 00:26:33,776
So if you file for divorce now,

521
00:26:34,857 --> 00:26:36,736
he'll have many ways
to handle this equity.

522
00:26:37,417 --> 00:26:38,137
And

523
00:26:38,697 --> 00:26:40,657
it will be difficult to get your share.

524
00:26:42,496 --> 00:26:45,016
I checked with insiders
at the listed company.

525
00:26:45,697 --> 00:26:48,096
They will decide within two months.

526
00:26:49,016 --> 00:26:52,377
So I suggest you wait a little longer.

527
00:26:54,776 --> 00:26:55,417
Two months?

528
00:26:56,336 --> 00:26:57,576
Another two months?

529
00:27:02,417 --> 00:27:03,536
I'm tired of waiting.

530
00:27:08,177 --> 00:27:09,256
I'm suffocating.

531
00:27:09,256 --> 00:27:10,336
Every time I see him,

532
00:27:10,336 --> 00:27:12,056
I want to scream curses at him

533
00:27:12,056 --> 00:27:13,536
and throw things in his face.

534
00:27:14,096 --> 00:27:15,697
I'm going crazy, you know?

535
00:27:16,256 --> 00:27:17,576
Yeah, I know.

536
00:27:17,857 --> 00:27:20,457
I understand how you feel right now.

537
00:27:21,697 --> 00:27:22,457
But

538
00:27:24,096 --> 00:27:27,056
we're talking about 15 million.

539
00:27:30,377 --> 00:27:31,857
Stop tempting me, Mr. Lai.

540
00:27:32,617 --> 00:27:33,457
Money is important,

541
00:27:33,937 --> 00:27:35,217
but my life matters more.

542
00:27:36,377 --> 00:27:38,336
Besides, even if I wait for him

543
00:27:38,336 --> 00:27:38,937
to cash out,

544
00:27:38,937 --> 00:27:40,816
will he share the money with me?

545
00:27:46,857 --> 00:27:47,816
I still want a divorce.

546
00:27:50,617 --> 00:27:52,977
Alright, you sound determined.

547
00:27:54,417 --> 00:27:57,377
Actually, I've prepared the agreement.

548
00:27:59,016 --> 00:27:59,937
Here, take a look.

549
00:28:06,312 --> 00:28:09,299
(Divorce Agreement)

550
00:28:24,056 --> 00:28:26,776
(How will Li Dongming react
when he sees the divorce agreement?)

551
00:28:28,336 --> 00:28:30,217
(Will he beg me to stay in tears?)

552
00:28:31,617 --> 00:28:32,137
(Zhao Mei.)

553
00:28:32,816 --> 00:28:33,496
(Don't be soft.)

554
00:28:33,977 --> 00:28:34,657
(Don't hesitate.)

555
00:28:35,336 --> 00:28:36,576
(Confront him right now.)

556
00:28:55,697 --> 00:28:56,857
You're home?

557
00:29:03,417 --> 00:29:04,872
Why didn't you turn on the lights?

558
00:29:09,256 --> 00:29:09,857
What's wrong?

559
00:29:11,576 --> 00:29:12,576
I might have cancer.

560
00:29:16,056 --> 00:29:17,457
Don't scare yourself.

561
00:29:18,177 --> 00:29:19,256
Did you get checked?

562
00:29:23,177 --> 00:29:26,137
The company organized a physical exam.

563
00:29:27,576 --> 00:29:30,576
The hospital called me today,

564
00:29:31,296 --> 00:29:35,296
saying a cancer indicator
came back abnormal.

565
00:29:37,977 --> 00:29:39,177
I asked someone I know.

566
00:29:41,697 --> 00:29:42,617
It's bad.

567
00:29:45,256 --> 00:29:46,137
Probably liver cancer.

568
00:29:48,177 --> 00:29:48,617
Zhao Mei.

569
00:29:51,816 --> 00:29:52,937
I'm only 39.

570
00:29:53,937 --> 00:29:55,417
I-I'm only 39.

571
00:29:55,697 --> 00:29:57,177
How could I get cancer?

572
00:29:57,177 --> 00:29:58,857
I'm only 39.

573
00:29:59,177 --> 00:30:00,697
How could I get cancer?

574
00:30:00,897 --> 00:30:02,256
It's okay.

575
00:30:04,177 --> 00:30:04,904
Don't be afraid.

576
00:30:05,177 --> 00:30:07,177
It's just an abnormal indicator.

577
00:30:07,657 --> 00:30:08,697
It's not diagnosed.

578
00:30:10,377 --> 00:30:11,177
In a few days...

579
00:30:11,736 --> 00:30:12,296
Tomorrow...

580
00:30:12,977 --> 00:30:16,697
Tomorrow, we'll try
another hospital, okay?

581
00:30:19,897 --> 00:30:21,177
That's what the doctor said.

582
00:30:21,417 --> 00:30:23,296
He told me to take a week off,

583
00:30:23,657 --> 00:30:24,617
adjust my schedule,

584
00:30:24,937 --> 00:30:27,576
and then get checked
at a bigger hospital.

585
00:30:27,576 --> 00:30:28,137
See?

586
00:30:29,177 --> 00:30:31,137
So rest at home for a few days.

587
00:30:34,496 --> 00:30:38,096
I've heard that certain situations
can raise those indicators.

588
00:30:38,096 --> 00:30:38,697
Like what?

589
00:30:39,177 --> 00:30:42,417
Things like drinking,
taking cold medicine,

590
00:30:42,417 --> 00:30:44,217
or staying up too late.

591
00:30:44,617 --> 00:30:45,977
But it's nothing permanent.

592
00:30:46,296 --> 00:30:48,816
Have you taken any medicine lately?

593
00:30:50,457 --> 00:30:55,417
Last week, I did take cold medicine
once and hangover medicine twice.

594
00:30:55,417 --> 00:30:56,697
There you go.

595
00:30:56,857 --> 00:30:58,457
It's likely the medicine.

596
00:31:00,496 --> 00:31:02,177
Relax for now.

597
00:31:03,137 --> 00:31:04,137
Stop scaring yourself.

598
00:31:04,897 --> 00:31:06,697
We'll go get it checked very soon.

599
00:31:06,897 --> 00:31:08,040
I'll make you some noodles.

600
00:31:10,417 --> 00:31:10,857
Zhao Mei.

601
00:31:12,576 --> 00:31:16,457
Could you maybe
skip the store rounds at night?

602
00:31:17,617 --> 00:31:18,496
Stay with me.

603
00:31:25,256 --> 00:31:25,857
I won't go.

604
00:31:28,217 --> 00:31:28,897
Promise?

605
00:31:30,096 --> 00:31:30,496
Come on.

606
00:31:31,536 --> 00:31:33,177
Let's get up first. Come on.

607
00:31:38,897 --> 00:31:40,256
Go on, take a shower.

608
00:31:40,977 --> 00:31:42,096
I'll make you some noodles.

609
00:31:42,857 --> 00:31:44,256
Go to bed early.

610
00:31:44,897 --> 00:31:45,897
Don't overthink it.

611
00:31:45,897 --> 00:31:47,617
You will stay? You promise?

612
00:31:54,697 --> 00:31:58,776
(I never imagined
things would take such a turn.)

613
00:31:59,736 --> 00:32:01,457
(I even had this malicious thought)

614
00:32:01,457 --> 00:32:03,816
(that Li Dongming
found out I wanted a divorce)

615
00:32:03,977 --> 00:32:05,576
(and pulled this stunt on purpose.)

616
00:32:07,177 --> 00:32:08,697
(But it didn't look like it.)

617
00:32:09,937 --> 00:32:12,457
(Forget it. It's basic decency.)

618
00:32:30,657 --> 00:32:31,457
Zhao Mei.

619
00:32:32,377 --> 00:32:32,977
Zhao Mei.

620
00:32:33,576 --> 00:32:34,256
Zhao Mei.

621
00:32:34,256 --> 00:32:35,296
I'm here.

622
00:32:36,576 --> 00:32:37,217
What's wrong?

623
00:32:43,016 --> 00:32:44,256
You scared me.

624
00:32:58,336 --> 00:32:59,697
This vermicelli roll is amazing.

625
00:33:00,857 --> 00:33:01,937
I never knew about it.

626
00:33:01,937 --> 00:33:03,400
It's like I missed out on a fortune.

627
00:33:05,256 --> 00:33:07,657
There's a huge line
outside this restaurant.

628
00:33:07,657 --> 00:33:09,937
Lots of people drove there
just to buy it.

629
00:33:10,657 --> 00:33:12,977
I set three alarms and finally woke up

630
00:33:12,977 --> 00:33:13,617
to get it.

631
00:33:17,417 --> 00:33:18,377
Why aren't you eating?

632
00:33:19,897 --> 00:33:21,417
I'm eating.

633
00:33:25,897 --> 00:33:26,457
Is it good?

634
00:33:27,657 --> 00:33:28,177
Yeah.

635
00:33:32,897 --> 00:33:36,016
It's the first time
we're having breakfast like this.

636
00:33:36,417 --> 00:33:37,256
Not really.

637
00:33:37,897 --> 00:33:40,096
Don't your parents come
to make us breakfast?

638
00:33:40,096 --> 00:33:41,457
I mean, just us two.

639
00:33:44,937 --> 00:33:45,697
Well, that's true.

640
00:33:47,417 --> 00:33:48,177
It's quite novel.

641
00:33:48,576 --> 00:33:49,496
Feels great.

642
00:33:50,417 --> 00:33:53,496
I hope we can do this often.

643
00:33:58,256 --> 00:34:00,016
You want me to get up at 6:30 AM

644
00:34:00,177 --> 00:34:01,697
and queue up to buy breakfast?

645
00:34:02,897 --> 00:34:04,096
I'll go. I'll queue up.

646
00:34:27,897 --> 00:34:30,136
When will the results be out?

647
00:34:30,937 --> 00:34:32,696
Two will be ready today.

648
00:34:32,696 --> 00:34:34,737
The other two will take 48 hours.

649
00:34:35,096 --> 00:34:38,216
They'll be on your phone.
Press it for five minutes.

650
00:34:39,457 --> 00:34:40,096
Thank you.

651
00:34:44,297 --> 00:34:45,337
Don't be paranoid.

652
00:34:45,937 --> 00:34:47,257
Didn't my friend say?

653
00:34:47,457 --> 00:34:48,737
If it were malignant,

654
00:34:48,737 --> 00:34:50,216
you'd have symptoms by now.

655
00:34:50,817 --> 00:34:52,297
But you're not in pain or anything.

656
00:34:52,737 --> 00:34:53,576
So it probably isn't.

657
00:34:55,016 --> 00:34:55,977
Worst-case scenario,

658
00:34:56,576 --> 00:34:57,496
even if you have it,

659
00:34:57,897 --> 00:34:59,136
it's very early stage.

660
00:34:59,536 --> 00:35:00,257
You'll be cured.

661
00:35:02,897 --> 00:35:04,176
I want to visit Xiao Yang.

662
00:35:05,457 --> 00:35:06,257
Xiao Yang?

663
00:35:07,216 --> 00:35:08,056
What about him?

664
00:35:08,897 --> 00:35:09,937
He has bladder cancer.

665
00:35:10,496 --> 00:35:12,136
He found it during this health check

666
00:35:12,136 --> 00:35:13,337
and just had surgery.

667
00:35:14,457 --> 00:35:16,817
Okay, go ahead.

668
00:35:16,817 --> 00:35:17,536
I won't go.

669
00:35:18,696 --> 00:35:19,977
We have a store nearby.

670
00:35:19,977 --> 00:35:20,656
I'll take a look.

671
00:35:29,257 --> 00:35:30,457
Don't be influenced.

672
00:35:31,857 --> 00:35:32,496
Think about it.

673
00:35:32,496 --> 00:35:33,297
How likely is it

674
00:35:33,937 --> 00:35:37,377
for two Senior Partners
to get cancer at the same time?

675
00:35:39,977 --> 00:35:40,576
I'm off.

676
00:35:43,216 --> 00:35:43,857
Zhao Mei.

677
00:36:22,257 --> 00:36:24,096
Why do you have your wife
clean up after you

678
00:36:24,857 --> 00:36:26,176
instead of hiring a caregiver?

679
00:36:26,576 --> 00:36:27,817
You think I didn't try?

680
00:36:28,696 --> 00:36:30,696
I had to make appointments
a month in advance.

681
00:36:30,897 --> 00:36:32,616
Where do I find one last minute?

682
00:36:36,176 --> 00:36:37,937
Want some coffee?

683
00:36:38,937 --> 00:36:39,696
Coffee?

684
00:36:39,737 --> 00:36:40,977
How come you have coffee here?

685
00:36:40,977 --> 00:36:41,737
Who drinks it?

686
00:36:42,016 --> 00:36:42,937
My wife.

687
00:36:44,496 --> 00:36:46,457
She sleeps on the couch.

688
00:36:47,257 --> 00:36:48,056
It's awful.

689
00:36:48,496 --> 00:36:50,937
She can't get through the day
without coffee.

690
00:36:50,937 --> 00:36:53,176
Your wife really has it tough.

691
00:36:53,937 --> 00:36:55,777
To think she cleans up after you.

692
00:36:56,297 --> 00:36:58,696
Not many people would do that nowadays.

693
00:36:58,696 --> 00:36:59,216
True.

694
00:37:01,016 --> 00:37:03,377
My wife has been through so much.

695
00:37:04,457 --> 00:37:07,576
This cancer has really opened my eyes.

696
00:37:08,977 --> 00:37:09,977
In this world,

697
00:37:10,857 --> 00:37:11,616
in this lifetime,

698
00:37:12,737 --> 00:37:16,817
only health and happiness truly matter.

699
00:37:17,737 --> 00:37:20,937
We've been busy
with projects and clients.

700
00:37:21,496 --> 00:37:22,937
It's just for money.

701
00:37:23,257 --> 00:37:24,297
We were buried in work,

702
00:37:25,777 --> 00:37:26,696
feeling like slaves.

703
00:37:27,176 --> 00:37:27,897
What's the point?

704
00:37:28,496 --> 00:37:29,216
It's pointless.

705
00:37:30,377 --> 00:37:33,096
Those are just karmic obstructions.

706
00:37:34,297 --> 00:37:35,897
You've had a profound awakening.

707
00:37:36,656 --> 00:37:37,937
I finally realized

708
00:37:38,777 --> 00:37:40,977
the meaning of true love.

709
00:37:43,616 --> 00:37:44,136
The drawer.

710
00:37:52,457 --> 00:37:53,937
This is true love.

711
00:37:55,897 --> 00:37:56,977
My wife is the example.

712
00:37:58,656 --> 00:38:01,857
When disaster struck, only she

713
00:38:02,737 --> 00:38:04,817
and you stood by me.

714
00:38:07,937 --> 00:38:08,737
Dongming,

715
00:38:09,656 --> 00:38:14,257
all those charming faces you see around
are nothing but monsters in disguise.

716
00:38:36,443 --> 00:38:41,183
♪All the stars are out tonight♪

717
00:38:45,633 --> 00:38:47,553
♪Too much of shame♪

718
00:38:47,899 --> 00:38:50,695
♪To waste it crying♪

719
00:38:53,153 --> 00:38:55,073
♪Leave all behind you♪

720
00:38:55,073 --> 00:38:57,353
♪Gotta go on to better things♪

721
00:38:57,473 --> 00:38:59,702
♪You know how far you've gone♪

722
00:38:59,837 --> 00:39:02,113
♪In the fire you rise again♪

723
00:39:02,299 --> 00:39:04,659
♪You made it through the worst♪

724
00:39:04,797 --> 00:39:07,001
♪The best is yet to come♪

725
00:39:07,244 --> 00:39:09,384
♪The best is yet to come♪

726
00:39:12,086 --> 00:39:13,409
♪Isn't it magical♪

727
00:39:13,409 --> 00:39:15,041
♪Listen, look,
how beautiful the night is♪

728
00:39:15,073 --> 00:39:17,540
♪With countless lights on,
is someone heartbroken again♪

729
00:39:17,540 --> 00:39:19,993
♪The sound of a heart
shattering on the ground is so crisp♪

730
00:39:20,074 --> 00:39:22,722
♪Turn on a light.
A lonely heart needs comfort♪

731
00:39:22,811 --> 00:39:25,342
♪Sweat, toil, dawn, dusk♪

732
00:39:25,422 --> 00:39:27,644
♪Devaluing self-respect
just for some hot food♪

733
00:39:27,786 --> 00:39:28,867
♪But I don't want to♪

734
00:39:28,976 --> 00:39:31,242
♪Sell dignity at a price,
trampling on past vows♪

735
00:39:31,358 --> 00:39:32,423
♪Until 3 AM♪

736
00:39:32,594 --> 00:39:33,799
♪Locking dreams away in a drawer♪

737
00:39:33,953 --> 00:39:35,186
♪Just to earn some meager profit♪

738
00:39:35,277 --> 00:39:37,641
♪No matter how hard I try,
it only brings sobs♪

739
00:39:37,788 --> 00:39:42,198
♪Renewing yearly, gone with no return,
teetering, utterly bland♪

740
00:39:56,923 --> 00:39:58,359
♪Leave all behind you♪

741
00:39:58,463 --> 00:40:00,950
♪Gotta go on to better things♪

742
00:40:01,133 --> 00:40:03,262
♪You know how far you've gone♪

743
00:40:03,449 --> 00:40:05,789
♪In the fire you rise again♪

744
00:40:05,857 --> 00:40:08,123
♪You made it through the worst♪

745
00:40:08,483 --> 00:40:10,561
♪The best is yet to come♪

746
00:40:10,810 --> 00:40:12,980
♪The best is yet to come♪

747
00:40:15,681 --> 00:40:16,833
♪Isn't it magical♪

748
00:40:16,833 --> 00:40:20,479
♪All the stars are out tonight♪

749
00:40:20,513 --> 00:40:22,369
♪And I see them sparkling♪

750
00:40:22,593 --> 00:40:24,724
♪Nobody knows♪

751
00:40:25,345 --> 00:40:27,255
♪What tomorrow brings♪

752
00:40:27,521 --> 00:40:29,844
♪You made it through the worst♪

753
00:40:30,031 --> 00:40:32,239
♪The best is yet to come♪

754
00:40:32,526 --> 00:40:34,675
♪The best is yet to come♪

755
00:40:34,971 --> 00:40:36,385
♪Isn't it magical♪

756
00:40:36,385 --> 00:40:38,597
♪Feeling uneasy,
yet no one's chasing me♪

757
00:40:38,671 --> 00:40:41,025
♪Retreating step by step,
everything turning to ash♪

758
00:40:41,025 --> 00:40:42,113
♪I'm silent, I'm roaring♪

759
00:40:42,113 --> 00:40:45,564
♪This helplessness
keeps pushing me towards the cliff♪

760
00:40:46,017 --> 00:40:48,291
♪Trembling legs
carry away a shattered soul♪

761
00:40:48,705 --> 00:40:49,569
♪Who wants to be just a passerby♪

762
00:40:49,569 --> 00:40:51,089
♪Isn't it magical♪
